::DrillBit::

DrillBit, now awake looked at KitKat.
"But..." He stoped. It was his place to protect her, but she was
Commander, and just gave him an order.
"Ok."
He climbed into StarScream.
"Ok, lets go. But dont go and land, lets stay close to the ship, just
encass we need to make a last minute rescue of KitKat. She can be
careless."
